result:
<a-modal
  :title="title"
  :visible="visible"
  :keyboard="false"
  :maskClosable="false"
  okText="保存"
  okType="primary"
  @ok="handleBuildOk()"
  @cancel="handleBuildCancel()">
  <a-form
    :form="form">
    <a-form-item
      label="新增列名"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
          'name',
          {
            rules: [
              { max:16, message: '长度在16个汉字以内' },
               {required: true, message: '请输入列名'}
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue:  null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
  </a-form>
</a-modal>
